    "def Butcher_solver(f,t,x,h,A,b,c):\n",
    "    Num_stages=len(c)\n",
    "    m=len(x)\n",
    "    k=np.zeros([Num_stages,m])\n",
    "    k[0]=f(t,x)\n",
    "    for i in range(1,Num_stages):\n",
    "        Sum=np.zeros([m])\n",
    "        for j in range(i):\n",
    "            Sum=Sum+A[i][j]*k[j,:]\n",
    "        k[i,:]=f(t+c[i]*h,x+h*Sum)    \n",
    "    F=x+h*np.dot(b,k)\n",
    "    return F"
   ]
  },

   "source": [

    "b_RK4=np.array([1/6.,1/3.,1/3.,1/6.])\n",

   ]

    "def two_body_problem(t,x):\n",
    "    y1,y2,y3,y4=x\n",
    "    dxy1=y3\n",
    "    dxy2=y4\n",
    "    dxy3=-y1/((y1**2+y2**2)**(3/2))\n",
    "    dxy4=-y2/((y1**2+y2**2)**(3/2))\n",
    "    return [dxy1,dxy2,dxy3,dxy4]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def Butcher_Stepper(f,t0,tf,y0,h,A,b,c):\n",
    "    m=len(y0)\n",
    "    n=int((tf-t0)/h)\n",
    "    sol=np.zeros([n,m])\n",
    "    sol[0]=y0\n",
    "    for i in range(1,n):\n",
    "        sol[i]=Butcher_solver(f,t0,sol[i-1],h,A,b,c)\n",
    "    T=np.linspace(t0,tf,n)\n",
    "    return sol,T"
   ]
  },

    "def Adaptive_Butcher(f,t,x,h,A,b,b_hat,c,p,Tol,Fs):\n",
    "    Num_stages=len(c)\n",
    "    m=len(x)\n",
    "    k=np.zeros([Num_stages,m])\n",
    "    k[0]=f(t,x)\n",
    "    for i in range(1,Num_stages):\n",
    "        Sum=np.zeros([m])\n",
    "        for j in range(i):\n",
    "            Sum=Sum+A[i][j]*k[j,:]\n",
    "        k[i,:]=f(t+c[i]*h,x+h*Sum)\n",
    "    F=x+h*np.dot(b,k)    \n",
    "    l=abs(h*np.dot(b_hat-b,k))\n",
    "    if l>Tol:\n",
    "        h=Fs*h*(Tol/l)**(1/(p+1))\n",
    "        return h,list(x),0\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        h=Fs*h*(Tol/l)**(1/(p+1))\n",
    "        return h,list(F),1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def Adaptive_Butcher_Stepper(f,t0,tf,y0,h,A,b,b_hat,c,p=2,Tol=1e-2,Fs=1):\n",
    "    t=t0\n",
    "    m=len(y0)\n",
    "    sol=[y0]\n",
    "    T=[t0]\n",
    "    i=1\n",
    "    while(t<tf):\n",
    "        h,solt,s=Adaptive_Butcher(f,t,sol[i-1],h,A,b,b_hat,c,p,Tol,Fs)\n",
    "        if s==1:\n",
    "            sol=sol+[solt]\n",
    "            t=t+h\n",
    "            i=i+1\n",
    "            T=T+[t]    \n",
    "    return sol,T"
   ]
  },

    "def Explicit_euler(ode_system,y0,tf,h=0.01,t0=0):\n",
    "    n=int((tf-t0)/h)\n",
    "    m=len(y0)\n",
    "    sol=np.zeros([n,m])\n",
    "    sol[0]=y0\n",
    "    for i in range(1,n):\n",
    "        sol[i]=sol[i-1]+h*ode_system(sol[i-1])\n",
    "    return sol"
   ]
  },

    "def PreyP(x):\n",

    "def PreyP_odeint(t,x):\n",
    "    x1,x2=x\n",

    "    return np.array([dx1,dx2])"
   ]

   "source": [
    "def Adams_Solver(ode_system,f,tf,h=0.01,t0=0):\n",
    "    n=int((tf-t0)/h)\n",
    "    m=len(f[0])\n",
    "    sol=np.zeros([n,m])\n",
    "    sol[0]=f[0]\n",
    "    sol[1]=f[1]\n",
    "    sol[2]=f[2]\n",
    "    for i in range(3,n):\n",
    "        sol[i]=sol[i-1]+h/12*(23*ode_system(sol[i-1])-16*ode_system(sol[i-2])+5*ode_system(sol[i-3]))\n",
    "    return sol"
   ]
